The package geo-utils-cpp provides CMake targets:

    find_package(GeoUtilsCpp CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE geo::utils)

Documentation:

    Getting started: https://github.com/gistrec/geo-utils-cpp/blob/master/docs/getting-started.md
    API reference:   https://github.com/gistrec/geo-utils-cpp/blob/master/docs/api.md
